{"tid":1688581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尖沙咀疑有警員被擲「屎彈」","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:17:27.000Z","uid":20933,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdbb142e50c0c8aaed73e282d7a5e4eef01a5aff","tid":1688581,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20191102_20191102-192441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20191102_20191102-192441.jpg&h=32328332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民發起下午在尖沙咀栢麗大道，舉行唱抗爭歌曲集會，早前已獲警方發出不反對通知書。集會晚上繼續進行，現場數百人聚集，舉起手機燈光唱歌。一批防暴警察在柏麗大道對面戒備。期間有人在行人路打鬥，防暴警察越過彌敦道，並一度沿彌敦道追截，現場亦出現懷疑汽油彈在路上燃燒。<br />\n<br />\n大會早前表示，傍晚約六時在柏麗大道對面，有警員被投擲「屎彈」，警方要求申請人呼籲人士不要作出襲警行為，以及保持集會人數不超過300人。其後大會要求大部分參與人士散開，部分人不理會，繼續集會；部分則在附近一帶徘徊，入夜後有人用鐳射筆照向戒備的警員，警方作出警告，又以強光反照向集會的人。"},{"pid":"31c9b211a7372ba3edfc8e45f6576cab8964ecb6","tid":1688581,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1199802&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1199802%26csid%3D261_341&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=5a21c92c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1199802&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a10f99e04c3215b7a2d8421b177859ee5f7ca1c0","tid":1688581,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫手retweet</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI